SUMMARY:School Board Recognition Month
DESCRIPTION:We encourage school districts\, education service districts\, community colleges\, mayors and other local officials to join OSBA in celebrating “School Board Recognition Month” in January. By doing so\, you can help educate citizens about the importance of public schools and the people who ensure that Oregon’s children receive the education they need to prosper in today’s global economy. Find resources here: https://www.osba.org/school-board-recognition-month-resources/ \n 
URL:https://www.osba.org/event/school-board-recognition-month-2-3/2026-01-01/
CATEGORIES:Events
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://www.osba.org/wp-content/uploads/2023-SB_Superhero_1100x480-ForOEN.png
END:VEVENT
