SUMMARY:National Assistant Principal Week
DESCRIPTION:Join the National Association of Secondary School Principals\, the National Association of Elementary School Principals and the American Federation of School Administrators in honoring the enormous contributions of assistant principals to student success. Find e-cards\, activity ideas and ways to show your appreciation during #APWEEK.
URL:https://www.osba.org/event/national-assistant-principal-week/2026-04-06/
CATEGORIES:Events
