SUMMARY:National School Nurse Day
DESCRIPTION:National School Nurse Day recognizes school nurses who work to improve the health and learning of students. The National Association of School Nurses provides social media graphics and information to help celebrate the contributions from school nurses. Use OSBA’s sample resolution to proclaim National School Nurse Day in your school or district.
URL:https://www.osba.org/event/national-school-nurse-day/2026-05-13/
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.osba.org/wp-content/uploads/NASN_-_School_Nurse_Day_LOGO_-_SMALL.jpg
END:VEVENT
