DESCRIPTION:The Oregon Rural School Board Members Caucus Leadership Assembly will meet on the third Tuesday of every month at 6:00 p.m. via Zoom. \nZoom meeting information will be distributed upon request. For more information\, please contact Tracy Adevai. \nOctober 20\, 2026\, ORSBMC Leadership Assembly Agenda \nPlease contact the OSBA Executive Assistant to request a sign language interpreter or other communication aid by phone\, 503-485-4834\, or email\, ltrissel@osba.org. All requests must be received at least 48 hours prior to the meeting.
URL:https://www.osba.org/event/oregon-rural-school-board-members-caucus-leadership-assembly-meeting-october/
