SUMMARY:OSBA Annual Membership Meeting
DESCRIPTION:The Oregon School Boards Association will hold its Annual Membership Meeting at a time yet to be determined on Saturday\, November 14\, 2026\, at the Portland Marriott Downtown Waterfront\, 1401 SW Naito Pkwy\, Portland\, OR 97201. \n  \nThe OSBA Board president and secretary-treasurer will provide a brief overview of the state of the association through a high-level update of the association’s activities and finances.  \n  \nOSBA Annual Membership Meeting Agenda \n  \nOSBA Treasurer’s Report \n  \nOSBA 2026-2027 Budget \n  \nPlease contact the OSBA Executive Assistant to request a sign language interpreter or other communication aid by phone\, 503-485-4834\, or email\, ltrissel@osba.org. All requests must be received at least 48 hours prior to the meeting. \n  \nFor more information contact La’Nell Trissel.
URL:https://www.osba.org/event/osba-annual-membership-meeting-3/
END:VEVENT
